---
description: Markdown File Rules
globs: **/*.md
alwaysApply: true
---

- Prefer headings over tables when the table would only have 2 columns
- Do not use `;` in sentances it is not common for people to use them
- After writing to a file, reread it before responding.
  If the user has since edited your output, treat their edits as **required** corrections and follow that style
  going forward
